      "chain_name": "Elasticsearch Query Injection \u2192 Client-Controlled Pricing \u2192 Missing Audit Logs \u2192 Data Modification",
      "attack_scenario": "An attacker uses Elasticsearch query_string syntax to broaden parking search results, books a premium spot with a client-controlled zero or negative total cost, and cancels bookings without an audit event.",
